{"tid":2338690,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"《華爾街日報》爆傳馬雲曾提出將部分螞蟻股權交予中國政府就出事","createTime":"2020-12-24T07:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T08:03:38.000Z","uid":288849,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8c49cf1d10b13077e2b8bcd1831e772a42360ada","tid":2338690,"uid":288849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"前幾日《華爾街日報》引述消息人士報道，阿里巴巴(<a href=\"http://09988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F09988.HK&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=ced2e58e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">09988.HK</a>)創始人馬雲曾在11月2日，即原定螞蟻集團上市前曾試圖挽回與北京的關係，在與監管機構的約談上提出將部分螞蟻集團股權轉交給中國政府。跟住今日就出事，罷明消息人士唔知會唔會係馬生果邊？你講到獻寶就搞掂，好似賄賂國家就OK，絕對影響國家高層清廉形象？而且呢啲嘢係會議秘密，洩漏出去，上面一定不滿，所以咪造低你？"},{"pid":"94aff09a6804f3ed0c4c9ebba12d4e41fd7479c3","tid":2338690,"uid":10905,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:31:53.000Z","msg":"我唔係要部分<br />\n我係要曬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04c9afe0ba9676d04780b65d3f4c1bc23c87bd1","tid":2338690,"uid":214502,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:32:02.000Z","msg":"支那:<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDNGCFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDNGCFh.jpg&h=0a69da6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a93c73dfdb67e25c3354f1af61d3b921be31ec1","tid":2338690,"uid":52946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:38:31.000Z","msg":"姐係比得唔夠多先出事"},{"pid":"e880046911ddca2484156eccc871aa16c0a36816","tid":2338690,"uid":268903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:43:26.000Z","msg":"其實不存在討價還價<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fedd1e013fbdce8ed72984c05d2aed3adb2004d","tid":2338690,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:43:39.000Z","msg":"我全都要.jpg"},{"pid":"e83a600cdf8f9c2a97327d0e6ff7a32a3eb3fb8e","tid":2338690,"uid"